was a bug there.

00:26:18.790 --> 00:26:21.060
I extracted it out into
its own function.

00:26:21.060 --> 00:26:22.770
I wrote a quick function
called test.

00:26:22.770 --> 00:26:25.510
And I did all my testing and
debugging within the scope of

00:26:25.510 --> 00:26:26.720
the script editor.

00:26:26.720 --> 00:26:28.180
Now, this gets you most
